videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Jordan Ratinho catches the inbounds pass and launches a triple that finds nothing but net.
videos.headline: Ratinho drains catch-and-shoot 3

videos.description: Jordan Hunter gets all of a block attempt sending the dunk off the backboard.
videos.headline: Hunter spikes ball off backboard for block

videos.description: Frankie Ferrari hits a 3 deep behind the arc to put San Francisco up 62-58 over Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Clutch 3 extends San Francisco's lead

videos.description: Down 62-58 late in the 2nd half, Jock Landale fouls out and finishes with 19 points.
videos.headline: Landale fouls out for Saint Mary's
